name: SatNet LEO Group 19
location_str: Commercial LC-2 @ Wenchang Space Launch Site, CHN
description: A batch of 9 Low Earth Orbit communication satellites for the Chinese state owned SatNet constellation operated by the China Satellite Network Group.  The constellation will eventually consists of 13000 satellites.
rocket_fact: Astronauts on the International Space Station witness 16 sunrises and sunsets every single day.
